JW2  C*  @PCON: CHECK PARENT CONSOLIDATED PACKING LIST
 |   C******************************************************
 |   C           @PCON     BEGSR
 |    * RETRIEVE PARENT PACK LIST#(#BAR2) FROM CHILD#
 |   C                     MOVELS2SERL    $BAR1
